asset.hookText:
August the 23th-26th, 2010, is ZERO and the Norwegian Automobile- Sport Federation organizing the 2010 Zero Emission rally. The 700 km rally runs along the Norwegian scenic coastline from Oslo to Stavanger, and will test the performance of hydrogen, plug- in hybrid and battery electric cars. Henning Solberg will participate in the rally, among with three Norwegian ministers.
